999999999999, "text": " Narrative is that I expect people to look at that and say, okay, it's going to go up", "tokens": [51052, 45658, 1166, 307, 300, 286, 2066, 561, 281, 574, 412, 300, 293, 584, 11, 1392, 11, 309, 311, 516, 281, 352, 493, 51208], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13138682625510475, "compression_ratio": 1.7478991596638656, "no_speech_prob": 0.02352321334183216}, {"id": 43, "seek": 19148, "start": 208.35999999999999, "end": 212.07999999999998, "text": " and they're already trying to buy right now, but their stop loss is going to be below that", "tokens": [51208, 293, 436, 434, 1217, 1382, 281, 2256, 558, 586, 11, 457, 641, 1590, 4470, 307, 516, 281, 312, 2507, 300, 51394], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13138682625510475, "compression_ratio": 1.7478991596638656, "no_speech_prob": 0.02352321334183216}, {"id": 44, "seek": 19148, "start": 212.07999999999998, "end": 213.07999999999998, "text": " swing low.", "tokens": [51394, 11173, 2295, 13, 51444], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13138682625510475, "compression_ratio": 1.7478991596638656, "no_speech_prob": 0.02352321334183216}, {"id": 45, "seek": 22148, "start": 221.79999999999998, "end": 226.32, "text": " So sell stops are resting at 13,614.", "tokens": [50380, 407, 3607, 10094, 366, 21221, 412, 3705, 11, 21, 7271, 13, 50606], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1569555523326096, "compression_ratio": 1.5043478260869565, "no_speech_prob": 0.07049885392189026}, {"id": 46, "seek": 22148, "start": 226.32, "end": 227.84, "text": " They just took those now.", "tokens": [50606, 814, 445, 1890, 729, 586, 13, 50682], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1569555523326096, "compression_ratio": 1.5043478260869565, "no_speech_prob": 0.07049885392189026}, {"id": 47, "seek": 22148, "start": 227.84, "end": 233.35999999999999, "text": " Now this is a high-risk entry long there, but I'm watching price now entering that same", "tokens": [50682, 823, 341, 307, 257, 1090, 12, 33263, 8729, 938, 456, 11, 457, 286, 478, 1976, 3218, 586, 11104, 300, 912, 50958], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1569555523326096, "compression_ratio": 1.5043478260869565, "no_speech_prob": 0.07049885392189026}, {"id": 48, "seek": 22148, "start": 233.35999999999999, "end": 235.6, "text": " fair value gap.", "tokens": [50958, 3143, 2158, 7417, 13, 51070], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1569555523326096, "compression_ratio": 1.5043478260869565, "no_speech_prob": 0.07049885392189026}, {"id": 49, "seek": 22148, "start": 235.6, "end": 242.83999999999997, "text": " So one more time to see if it wants to poke a little bit lower, and again, my daily bias", "tokens": [51070, 407, 472, 544, 565, 281, 536, 498, 309, 2738, 281, 19712, 257, 707, 857, 3126, 11, 293, 797, 11, 452, 5212, 12577, 51432], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1569555523326096, "compression_ratio": 1.5043478260869565, "no_speech_prob": 0.07049885392189026}, {"id": 50, "seek": 22148, "start": 242.83999999999997, "end": 246.07999999999998, "text": " is bullish, so I'm looking for higher prices.", "tokens": [51432, 307, 38692, 11, 370, 286, 478, 1237, 337, 2946, 7901, 13, 51594], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1569555523326096, "compression_ratio": 1.5043478260869565, "no_speech_prob": 0.07049885392189026}, {"id": 51, "seek": 22148, "start": 246.07999999999998, "end": 250.51999999999998, "text": " So I'm going to go and aim for the 80 level.", "tokens": [51594, 407, 286, 478, 516, 281, 352, 293, 5939, 337, 264, 4688, 1496, 13, 51816], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1569555523326096, "compression_ratio": 1.5043478260869565, "no_speech_prob": 0.07049885392189026}, {"id": 52, "seek": 25052, "start": 250.56, "end": 254.48000000000002, "text": " That'll give me a nice figure to run to $50,000 on equity.", "tokens": [50366, 663, 603, 976, 385, 257, 1481, 2573, 281, 1190, 281, 1848, 2803, 11, 1360, 322, 10769, 13, 50562], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.25929005940755206, "compression_ratio": 1.4285714285714286, "no_speech_prob": 0.007128824479877949}, {"id": 53, "seek": 25052, "start": 254.48000000000002, "end": 257.40000000000003, "text": " I do believe it's going to go higher, but I'm on vacation, so I want to kind of like", "tokens": [50562, 286, 360, 1697, 309, 311, 516, 281, 352, 2946, 11, 457, 286, 478, 322, 12830, 11, 370, 286, 528, 281, 733, 295, 411, 50708], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.25929005940755206, "compression_ratio": 1.4285714285714286, "no_speech_prob": 0.007128824479877949}, {"id": 54, "seek": 25052, "start": 257.40000000000003, "end": 265.36, "text": " let me take this long entry, and there you go.", "tokens": [50708, 718, 385, 747, 341, 938, 8729, 11, 293, 456, 291, 352, 13, 51106], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.25929005940755206, "compression_ratio": 1.4285714285714286, "no_speech_prob": 0.007128824479877949}, {"id": 55, "seek": 25052, "start": 265.36, "end": 274.76, "text": " All right, so now I'm watching price, and I want to see it expand up.", "tokens": [51106, 1057, 558, 11, 370, 586, 286, 478, 1976, 3218, 11, 293, 286, 528, 281, 536, 309, 5268, 493, 13, 51576], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.25929005940755206, "compression_ratio": 1.4285714285714286, "no_speech_prob": 0.007128824479877949}, {"id": 56, "seek": 27476, "start": 274.76, "end": 281.84, "text": " Now because it's the opening, and I don't know where if we whip below that low, I'll", "tokens": [50364, 823, 570, 309, 311, 264, 5193, 11, 293, 286, 500, 380, 458, 689, 498, 321, 22377, 2507, 300, 2295, 11, 286, 603, 50718], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16691423562856822, "compression_ratio": 1.8038461538461539, "no_speech_prob": 0.04196012020111084}, {"id": 57, "seek": 27476, "start": 281.84, "end": 288.24, "text": " give it a chance to go below it just by a little bit, and I'll close it at market.", "tokens": [50718, 976, 309, 257, 2931, 281, 352, 2507, 309, 445, 538, 257, 707, 857, 11, 293, 286, 603, 1998, 309, 412, 2142, 13, 51038], "tempera