: 303.24, "end": 310.6, "text": " I'm right here ready to click and close it if it trades below it, and I want to see it", "tokens": [50376, 286, 478, 558, 510, 1919, 281, 2052, 293, 1998, 309, 498, 309, 21287, 2507, 309, 11, 293, 286, 528, 281, 536, 309, 50744], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17492417820164416, "compression_ratio": 1.4589041095890412, "no_speech_prob": 0.011885088868439198}, {"id": 64, "seek": 30300, "start": 310.6, "end": 318.04, "text": " expand up.", "tokens": [50744, 5268, 493, 13, 51116], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17492417820164416, "compression_ratio": 1.4589041095890412, "no_speech_prob": 0.011885088868439198}, {"id": 65, "seek": 30300, "start": 318.04, "end": 323.76, "text": " Now I want to see an energetic run above the swing high that was formed just to the left", "tokens": [51116, 823, 286, 528, 281, 536, 364, 24935, 1190, 3673, 264, 11173, 1090, 300, 390, 8693, 445, 281, 264, 1411, 51402], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17492417820164416, "compression_ratio": 1.4589041095890412, "no_speech_prob": 0.011885088868439198}, {"id": 66, "seek": 30300, "start": 323.76, "end": 326.72, "text": " of where we are right now.", "tokens": [51402, 295, 689, 321, 366, 558, 586, 13, 51550], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17492417820164416, "compression_ratio": 1.4589041095890412, "no_speech_prob": 0.011885088868439198}, {"id": 67, "seek": 32672, "start": 326.72, "end": 334.84000000000003, "text": " There is a fair value gap at the 680 level, and it's above equilibrium, so it would be", "tokens": [50364, 821, 307, 257, 3143, 2158, 7417, 412, 264, 1386, 4702, 1496, 11, 293, 309, 311, 3673, 15625, 11, 370, 309, 576, 312, 50770], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2123459132030757, "compression_ratio": 1.5251141552511416, "no_speech_prob": 0.07450520992279053}, {"id": 68, "seek": 32672, "start": 334.84000000000003, "end": 341.40000000000003, "text": " a premium market, so that's why I'm going to be targeting the 80 level, plus it's around", "tokens": [50770, 257, 12049, 2142, 11, 370, 300, 311, 983, 286, 478, 516, 281, 312, 17918, 264, 4688, 1496, 11, 1804, 309, 311, 926, 51098], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2123459132030757, "compression_ratio": 1.5251141552511416, "no_speech_prob": 0.07450520992279053}, {"id": 69, "seek": 32672, "start": 341.40000000000003, "end": 345.76000000000005, "text": " 50 handles, so that gives me about $1,000 or more.", "tokens": [51098, 2625, 18722, 11, 370, 300, 2709, 385, 466, 1848, 16, 11, 1360, 420, 544, 13, 51316], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2123459132030757, "compression_ratio": 1.5251141552511416, "no_speech_prob": 0.07450520992279053}, {"id": 70, "seek": 32672, "start": 345.76000000000005, "end": 353.12, "text": " All right, so now, right now, at this moment, I want to see it expand aggressively, not", "tokens": [51316, 1057, 558, 11, 370, 586, 11, 558, 586, 11, 412, 341, 1623, 11, 286, 528, 281, 536, 309, 5268, 32024, 11, 406, 51684], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2123459132030757, "compression_ratio": 1.5251141552511416, "no_speech_prob": 0.07450520992279053}, {"id": 71, "seek": 32672, "start": 353.12, "end": 354.12, "text": " dilly dally around.", "tokens": [51684, 274, 6917, 274, 379, 926, 13, 51734], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2123459132030757, "compression_ratio": 1.5251141552511416, "no_speech_prob": 0.07450520992279053}, {"id": 72, "seek": 35412, "start": 354.12, "end": 369.56, "text": " I want to see it really try to spread its wings and take off and start moving.", "tokens": [50364, 286, 528, 281, 536, 309, 534, 853, 281, 3974, 1080, 11405, 293, 747, 766, 293, 722, 2684, 13, 51136], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16158501942952475, "compression_ratio": 1.483695652173913, "no_speech_prob": 0.04023786261677742}, {"id": 73, "seek": 35412, "start": 369.56, "end": 374.0, "text": " There's a small little fair value gap in the last three candles up.", "tokens": [51136, 821, 311, 257, 1359, 707, 3143